{
  "id": "adv_group_tri_04_05",
  "title": "TRINITYAiLE 04 05",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_05-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "（セミファイナル）\n（パフォーマンスが始まってすぐ、思い知らされた）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(The semifinals.)\n(As soon as the performance started‚ it hit me.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.083289996060458,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_05-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "（サニーピースのみんなは）\n（もう、私達よりも高い場所にいるんだ、と）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Sunny Peace)\n(are already in a higher place than us.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.105396652221678,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_05-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "（でも、だからこそ私達は、嬉しかった）\n（まだまだ成長出来るって可能性を、見つけられたから）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(But‚ that's why we were happy.)\n(Because we discovered the possibility that we can still grow.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.53872998555502,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gpstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 21.638729985554985
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_05-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "（長瀬麻奈に縛られることのない、まだ見ぬ高みへ）\n（自らの翼で羽ばたいていける、その可能性を……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(To unseen heights‚ free from the constraints of Nagase Mana.)\n(The possibility of soaring on our own wings…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.672063318888352,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 31.305396652221688
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 31.305396652221688
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "朝倉恭一",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kyoichi",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "…………いいステージだった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…………It was a good performance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.33872998555502,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 33.84936487674716
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_05-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "えっ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.98269821008047,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 34.88269821008046
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "朝倉恭一",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kyoichi",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "いいアイドルになったな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You've become a good idol.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.88269821008046,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_05-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "（表情を変えずにそれだけを言って、立ち去っていく）\n（その人の背中を眺めながら、言葉が零れた）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(He said only those words without changing his expression and walked away.)\n(As I watched his retreating figure‚ the words escaped my lips.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.05990906556448,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 45.19324239889781
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_05-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "……パパ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Dad…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.52657573223114,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 47.09324239889781
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_05-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "……瑠依ちゃん……良かったなあ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Rui-chan… I'm so happy for you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.09324239889781,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 51.0079815308253
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_05-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "瑠～依ちゃん……えへへ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ru~i-chan… Ehehe",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.0079815308253,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 53.735827438036566
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_05-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "……うん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yeah.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.7358274380366,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 55.06916077136996
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_05-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "（私の中に芽生えたこの感情を）\n（私はうまく言葉に出来なかった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(This feeling that has sprouted within me‚)\n(I couldn't quite put into words.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.76916077136994,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 60.335827438036596
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_05-rui010.m4a",
      "text": "（それでも、側にいる二人とは、分かち合えている）\n（今はそれで、十分だって思えた）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(But I'm sharing it with the two people beside me.)\n(I felt that was enough for now.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.70249410470328,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg3",
      "startTime": 69.1691607713699
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg3",
      "startTime": 69.16916077136993
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_05-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "とはいえ……負けてしまった事実は変わらんし\nサニピのみんな、さすがやわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But still… the fact that we lost remains unchanged‚\nand Sunny Peace‚ they're amazing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.40249410470325,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg3",
      "startTime": 77.42301501620045
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_05-rui011.m4a",
      "text": "ええ\n誰かを追いかけるのは止めて、自分達の道を行く",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes.\nThey stopped chasing someone and walked their own path.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.62397853223715,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg3",
      "startTime": 82.81353831478188
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_05-rui012.m4a",
      "text": "それだけで、こんなにも\n圧倒的なパフォーマンスを発揮出来るのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And just by doing that‚ they were able to deliver\nsuch an overwhelming performance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.71353831478191,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg3",
      "startTime": 87.58020498144857
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_05-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "そう思うと、なんだか勉強になったよね！\n明日からのレッスンで、また活かせそうかも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thinking about it that way‚ I feel like I learned something!\nI might be able to use it in lessons from tomorrow.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.14687164811524,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg3",
      "startTime": 94.31353831478184
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_05-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "そうやなぁ、これで終わった訳ちゃう\nアイドルとしては、まだまだ始まったばっかりやし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're right‚ it's not over yet.\nAs idols‚ we're just getting started.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.61353831478183,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg3",
      "startTime": 102.41353831478183
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_05-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "うん！　今日のことはしっかり反省して\nこれまで以上に頑張っていこうね、三人で！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah! Let's reflect on today\nand work even harder from now on‚ the three of us!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.31353831478177,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg3",
      "startTime": 108.4468716481147
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_05-rui013.m4a",
      "text": "ええ、もちろん\n私達は、まだまだ上を目指せるって分かった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ of course.\nWe know that we can still aim higher.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.51353831478174,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg3",
      "startTime": 113.81353831478174
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_05-rui014.m4a",
      "text": "なら、立ち止まっている暇はないもの\n今度こそ、誰にも負けない……そんな、自分達に……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then we don't have time to stand still.\nThis time‚ we won't lose to anyone… We'll become that kind of…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.2468716481151,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_05-rui015.m4a",
      "text": "……っ……はあ……でも、やっぱり……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Ugh… Sigh …But‚ still…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.88881927498883,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg3",
      "startTime": 123.8888192749892
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_05/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_05-rui017.m4a",
      "text": "…………悔しいなあ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…………I'm so frustrated…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.1888194657237,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg3",
      "startTime": 130.18881946572395
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg3",
      "startTime": 133.77133637436893
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
